dcterms:description: A large public fundus image benchmark for diabetic retinopathy (DR) grading and quality assessment, containing 12,543 training and 16,249 testing images. Based on image quality and DR severity, the images are classified into three quality categories and five severity levels.
dcterms:title: EyeQ

dcterms:description: Obtained from the public NIH-ChestXray14 multi-label dataset, it contains 8,573 training and 7,007 frontal X-ray images. The dataset includes two quality labels: high and low, and eight disease types.
dcterms:title: Chest X-ray
